[04/06/2018 00:32:48] <font color="#ffffff">para comprarte un piso</font>
[04/06/2018 00:32:50] <font color="#ffffff">y darte una sorpresa, Cristi.</font>
[04/06/2018 00:32:52] <font color="#ffffff">-Me la has dado.</font>
[04/06/2018 00:32:56] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Me crees, mi amor?</font>
